&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在线编程：&lt;a href=&#34;https://leetcode.com/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;LeetCode&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&#34;https://projecteuler.net/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Project Euler&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.codingame.com/start&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;CodingGame&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.kaggle.com/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Kaggle&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.topcoder.com/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Topcoder&lt;/a&gt;、牛客网、&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.hackerrank.com/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;HackerRank&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&#34;https://jsfight.club/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;JS Fight&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
